{"tid":1560674,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【本土研究社】今日最大假新聞：民建聯支持用《收回土地條例》起公屋","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:16:08.000Z","uid":138409,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a9373a4de6ba6799102c20afae0026e7cdf7ba7c","tid":1560674,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAtu49P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAtu49P.jpg&h=6f0953c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家睇番清楚民建聯8月29日發表既土地政綱(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2kbkJoN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kbkJoN&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=42a55d0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2kbkJoN</a> )。佢係話：<br />\n<br />\n(2)...政府應積極推動新發展區及公營房屋項目的規劃，並按《收回土地條例》賦予的權力，徵收發展所需的土地，加快土地供應。<br />\n<br />\n然後再補充番話：<br />\n<br />\n(4) 盡快公佈<span style=\"color: gold;\">「土地共享先導計劃」</span>詳情 [即公私合營與地產商合作] ，並主動規劃先導計劃的選址，再邀請業權人參與......<span style=\"color: gold;\">若合適的土地無法透過公私合作落實</span>，當局應引用《收回土地條例》收地自行發展。<br />\n<br />\n即係咩? 佢唔係冇條件支持用《收回土地條例》，<span style=\"color: gold;\">而係地產商囤積既農地係會先用「公私合營」拍著上，攪唔惦先建議會用徵地既方式。同佢走出黎大大聲走出黎登頭版廣告，話支持動用《收回土地條例》起公屋好唔同呀。</span><br />\n<br />\n即係民建聯依家可以透過一個假新聞廣告民意又要拎，地產商又要益、政府條line又要跟，一箭三雕，只需要喺個傳媒輿論煲大自己係支持收地，唔講收地既前提係先幫地產商釋放囤積農地起豪宅，用唔到啲生態敏感地 (如南生圍)、小地主既地，先至會靠政府收。<br />\n<br />\n講到自己咁大膽用土收，你估民建聯夠唔夠膽話「直接」用土收收哂發展商啲新界農地?<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，今日個結果梗係地產股升到嘭嘭聲啦，又扮勇武講用公權力收地，其實又係向地產商跪低利益輸送，根本唔敢收地產商上1,000公頃新界農地土儲，分分鐘可以透過收地產商囤開啲地邊邊做公屋，隨便起路俾地產商釋放隔離既囤地起巨型豪宅，元朗橫洲綠化帶益新世界同粉嶺皇后山隔離益恆基就係例子。<br />\n<br />\n所以證明左一樣野，就係現屆林鄭政府，或者呢個唔係向市民負責既政體，根本就已經俾地產商綁架著，未來話要解決房屋既深層次問題，就只可以扮做野而係冇辦法真正解決。<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n☕️【收地研究】改土歸流：下落不明的《收回土地條例》（文：黃肇鴻、陳劍青）- 20180615 明報觀點 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lNBbw0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lNBbw0&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=699aa918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lNBbw0</a><br />\n<br />\n💪 【揭破土地謊言好重要】月捐支持本研社土地研究工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5ca0fbe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a>"},{"pid":"95cdc990dbd89b16b4da6a67d5522ecdd7ee9d97","tid":1560674,"uid":41161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b121296bd1ec0c82cf75b7d27047f0c30c0140f","tid":1560674,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ef5c3e64ba1bc3ff163e55ea4f663235cce974b9","tid":1560674,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b091ccefca0e27cb883432bfcecf4e47f049c4c6","tid":1560674,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78ddb0e3123008b41db5db0fa86